{"tid":89861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]休班警偷拍16歲少女裙底","createTime":"2017-01-21T15:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T16:24:28.000Z","uid":1858,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2dcbca7480c050dcc22b5a5071716aaea9e8fa56","tid":89861,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:45:07.000Z","msg":"休班警港鐵旺角站偷拍16歲女裙底春斷正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n休班警港鐵旺角站偷拍裙底春斷正！一名姓邢(33歲)休班男警員，今午約3時許，被巡邏警員發現在港鐵旺角站一處扶手電梯，懷疑用手機偷拍前面一名16歲少女的裙底春光，巡警立刻截停他調查，並以涉嫌在公眾地方行為不檢將他拘捕，現正被扣查。據悉，涉案警員駐守水警西分區，是巡邏小隊的軍裝警員。 <br />\n<br />\n警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/news/mobile/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fnews%2Fmobile%2Findex.html&d=7oUeHtA8e%2FA4v5G%2FuKLHJZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=dc73495f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/news/mobile/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n休班警+1"},{"pid":"644fa7b24d5ead19105fa55a7d4d24c07f2eeb48","tid":89861,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"又係休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10091ed1d63f477b5ea27f20c96715e043ab6ecf","tid":89861,"uid":3098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:46:06.000Z","msg":"休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6517437a73d44092a7d47983660353475d8bf2f2","tid":89861,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:46:37.000Z","msg":"In休班警  we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a68db29d57bd20eb877e3858f2c4658167cad99","tid":89861,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"又係個別事件啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.g